                "actions": {
                    "value": 1
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per round</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The stalkers reach out to Grab their foes and drag them underwater. Each enemy in a @Template[type:emanation|distance:5] must succeed at a @Check[type:reflex|dc:33] save or be @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Grabbed] by the stalkers (or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Restrained] on a critical success). For the rest of the current turn, the saltborn stalkers can move toward water or in water without ending the grab, carrying any grabbed or restrained creatures along with them.</p>"
