                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per round</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The saltborn stalkers use their teeth and claws to vivisect each enemy within 5 feet (@Check[type:reflex|dc:30|basic:true] save). The damage depends on the number of actions.</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> @Damage[2d10[slashing]] damage</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">2</span> @Damage[(3d10+8)[slashing]] damage</p>\n<p><span class=\"action-glyph\">3</span> @Damage[(3d10+16)[slashing]] damage</p>"
